Carat is the most well-known diamond trait, and it refers to the weight of the diamond.  Clarity is measure of the imperfections (often referred to as “inclusions”) the diamond has.  Cut is what makes the diamond sparkle.  The better the cut, the more the stone with sparkle. Follow our Facebook page to find specials on our current collection, including vintage and UNOde50.  Our UNOde50 carries something for everyone that wants that piece that makes a statement.  This includes men’s bracelet made in Spain with braided leather and silver-plated clasps.  We have vintage jewelry that includes pieces from Tiffany & Co that will make that special someone feel on top of the world.  Give a sterling silver bead chain necklace with a heart pendant, or a sterling silver mesh ring.  Our complete collection is unlike anything you will ever find and our pieces are top quality. Full Description: Denver Concepts has stormed the scene with their upbeat, high energy work atmosphere and their unmatched drive for success! This business consulting and sales firm exceeds their client’s goals while providing professional growth opportunities to their employees.  The environment within this Denver office is electric! From their daily team meetings to their weekly after work get-togethers, the team comradery is like none other. Walking into the office in the morning is not like you would expect. The music is up loud, there are happy faces everywhere and everyone is anxiously waiting to start their day. You can’t help but be in a good mood when you start your day this way! After work, once a week (and more if you want) the team gets together at a local spot to literally just hang out. The best part is that it’s optional…and almost everyone is in attendance! That speaks loudly to the type of relationship these coworkers have. It all starts with the people that make up the Denver Concepts team. They come from all walks of life, educational backgrounds, and professional experience but they share one thing: a personal drive to be successful. All employees are required to start in the same entry level position within the company, receive the same type of training and mentoring, and then what they do with the opportunity that they are given is up to them! The reason behind this is the tried and true philosophy that the ‘cream rises to the top’. Typically, someone with high integrity, a strong will to succeed, a desire to help others and a commitment to ongoing learning excels, and rises up the ladder quickly, with this company.  With a team that has a personal mission to help one another succeed, a client that is as big as they come, and a management staff that is willing to do whatever it takes with integrity… there is not much that will get in the way of Denver Concepts. They are on their way to being the preferred vendor when it comes to business consulting needs in the metro Denver area and we recommend connecting with them on LinkedIn to keep up with their success story.
